BENEVOLENT FUND?

41:17.776 --> 41:20.712
- I THOUGHT YOU'D WANT TO KNOW
I WENT TO HIS APARTMENT.

41:20.746 --> 41:23.849
- WELL, YOU DIDN'T
WASTE ANY TIME, FOR ONCE.

41:23.882 --> 41:25.584
- LANDLORD THOUGHT
THE KID SKIPPED OUT

41:25.617 --> 41:27.152
WITHOUT PAYING HIS RENT.

41:27.185 --> 41:29.254
- THE KID'S NAME IS JASON.

41:29.287 --> 41:33.058
- HMM. HE'D ONLY BEEN HERE
A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

41:33.091 --> 41:35.260
YOU SHOULD
SEE HIS PLACE.

41:35.293 --> 41:37.896
NO FURNITURE, NOTHING.
JUST A MATTRESS.

41:37.929 --> 41:40.532
- DID YOU FIND HIS MOTHER?
- YES, MA'AM.

41:40.566 --> 41:43.802
SHE OD'D IN TAMPA
WHEN HE WAS FOUR.

41:43.835 --> 41:45.937
HE WAS SENT
TO FOSTER HOMES.

41:45.971 --> 41:49.875
