INCREDIBLE BAKED RIGATONI.

41:59.718 --> 42:03.121
- THANKS, I HAVE
TO GET BACK TO WORK.

42:08.694 --> 42:12.030
- WELL, IT WAS VERY
KIND OF YOU TO COME BY.

42:12.063 --> 42:15.967
- I THOUGHT
YOU'D LIKE TO KNOW.

42:16.001 --> 42:20.772
- YOU SURE YOU
WOULDN'T LIKE TO--

42:20.806 --> 42:24.776
- I'LL KEEP YOU POSTED
IF I FIND OUT ANYTHING ELSE.

42:24.810 --> 42:27.746
- DO THAT.

